                                            },
                                            "Text": {
                                                "val": "Will fund authorized civilian salaries and associated expenses (supplies, equipment, travel, etc.) at USAMRDC and USAMRAA. Also will provide regulatory, clinical monitoring and data support for the SIP. This program will provide non-licensed vaccines under FDA oversight to personnel at risk of exposure to selected infectious diseases."
